<h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
<p>Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website. They help the website function correctly and can provide information about how the site is used.</p>

<h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
<p>Executive Dating uses a limited number of cookies for the purposes described below.</p>

