      <td>Required for the website to function correctly, including form submission and navigation.</td>
      <td>No — these are strictly necessary.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Analytics cookies</td>
      <td>Anonymous data about how visitors use the site (e.g. pages viewed, time spent). We use Google Analytics for this purpose.</td>
