    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Preference cookies</td>
      <td>Remember your cookie consent choice to avoid showing the banner repeatedly.</td>
      <td>No — these store your own preference.</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
<p>We use Google Analytics, which may set cookies on your device to collect anonymous usage data. This data is processed in accordance with Google's privacy policies. We do not use advertising cookies or track you across other websites.</p>

<h2>4. Your Choices</h2>
<p>You can control or disable non-essential cookies in the following ways:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Using the cookie banner displayed when you first visit this website;</li>
  <li>Adjusting the cookie or privacy settings in your browser;</li>
  <li>Using your browser's "Do Not Track" feature (where supported).</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect the functionality of this website.</p>

<h2>5. Contact</h2>
<p>If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at <a href="mailto:executivedating08@gmail.com">executivedating08@gmail.com</a>.</p>

